org.goldenorb.queue
Class InboundMessageQueue

java.lang.Object
  org.goldenorb.queue.InboundMessageQueue

public class InboundMessageQueue
extends Object

This class provides a Queue construct that collects inbound messages for a partition. After a certain number of messages is collected, it sends out the messages to the appropriate destination vertices.
